Classes in org.jaudiotagger.tag.virtual used by org.jaudiotagger.audio
VirtualMetaDataContainer
          A VirtualMetaDataContainer can hold data from any tag type and can be used to convert between tags The tag format cannot currently be persisted to file it is intended for use in memory to allow the processing of tags by other applications through a common interface without having to know the internal workings of different audio types.
